### Payment Service API Tests

### 1. Initiate Payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": 1,
  "carId": 1,
  "buyerId": 2,
  "sellerId": 1,
  "amount": 550000,
  "method": "UPI",
  "remarks": "Payment for Maruti Swift"
}

### 2. Process Payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/1/process

### 3. Complete Payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/1/complete

### 4. Get Payment by ID
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/1

### 5. Get Payments by Buyer
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/buyer/2

### 6. Get Payments by Seller
GET http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/seller/1

### 7. Refund Payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/1/refund

### 8. Initiate Credit Card Payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": 2,
  "carId": 2,
  "buyerId": 3,
  "sellerId": 1,
  "amount": 750000,
  "method": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "remarks": "Payment for Honda City"
}

### 9. Initiate EMI Payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": 3,
  "carId": 3,
  "buyerId": 4,
  "sellerId": 2,
  "amount": 1200000,
  "method": "EMI",
  "remarks": "EMI payment for Hyundai Creta"
}
